{"tid":873631,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解成日都要攞丙朗同小花嚟做比較呢？","createTime":"2018-10-23T14:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T15:34:53.000Z","uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be46f8e4a10026bdc4d746b291e98343c653fb88","tid":873631,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"美斯同c朗兩個都係球王 即使球品點樣 技術點樣 我地都唔可以否認佢地嘅努力同能力<br />\n<br />\n兩個人互相都好欣賞對方 某程度上 分出小花派同丙朗派都係因為啲球迷覺得世上只可以有一個球王 所以小花迷就憎丙朗 丙朗迷就憎小花<br />\n<br />\n我自己係小花迷 但唔會因為我鍾意小花 就一定要憎丙朗 一定要唱鳩佢有幾廢 咁樣只會顯得你小花嘅球迷質素差<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日攞兩個球王做比較真係好無謂 因為兩個一樣咁勁 各有各技術特點 無得相提並論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1fjGVp0M80tSs9xLFj/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1fjGVp0M80tSs9xLFj%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b9f671f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38e09cad1a1cf1488d59a586f8aea1c7c5cdb010","tid":873631,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:56:07.000Z","msg":"小花嘅球迷質素差<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebdfb59d912675db433d03c59d8ddc3343546c0","tid":873631,"uid":34419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"牙朗新類型球員"},{"pid":"8aa725aacf7b5009d1ef414ce53cd3a58db967c2","tid":873631,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"樓主是垃圾"},{"pid":"0cabccdb1292015b3d08b90f89db6145d99c0505","tid":873631,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aa725aacf7b5009d1ef414ce53cd3a58db967c2","tid":873631,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"樓主是垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"唔同飲醉嘅人做朋友"},{"pid":"3e213e30b97e7813eb37602d8734fe4146f9859e","tid":873631,"uid":442